{"id": 2420, "genre": 1000, "title": "对社交网络失去兴趣的你是啥样的？", "description": "戒网瘾？不存在的，要是能把微信关掉微博注销就好了。（题图来自：视觉中国 © Shujie Selected RF）", "record_count": 15992, "comment_count": 52, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201806201618260jhr3IoJg2RqYTni.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-06-27T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 4390, "title": "对社交网络失去兴趣的你是啥样的？", "content": "现如今，哪些迹象证明你对社交网络失去兴趣了？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 287211, "content": "朋友圈屏蔽不看和不给 ta 看的人都越来越多", "image": "img/option/option/20180619173725GOWd48c3hoEIgwaq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 287212, "content": "主动发原创内容越来越少，最多分享链接", "image": "img/option/option/20180620164750bLUvDaWmi26g59Oc.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 287213, "content": "关闭了朋友圈的提醒小红点，眼不见为净", "image": "img/option/option/20180620163208oVcwG7YU5bQuv91T.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 287214, "content": "会推送“今日热门”的社交平台推送都关了", "image": "img/option/option/20180620163217ZAPFScB9kNJqzI2u.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 287215, "content": "清理微博、豆瓣的关注，删掉一多半", "image": "img/option/option/20180620165428PegxYopmnc8CvV3z.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 287216, "content": "之前很在意微博粉丝，现在只想用工具移除僵尸粉", "image": "img/option/option/20180620163243aGPzUMh3QNl7keDL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 287217, "content": "闭关工作、论文的时候不再需要刻意戒断刷社交网络了", "image": "img/option/option/20180620164713li8WSmtorxhuykJC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 287218, "content": "常混的小组、贴吧不知道什么时候开始就不看了", "image": "img/option/option/20180620164313dyc2fAXF0PtuW3oV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}